column2: "How is it, are you able to trace Hadred?"
"Looks like you haven't found anything yet."
"I can tell by the expression by looking at your face. Don't worry it's like tracking something like me."
"But I won't give up, not until I kill that traitor with my own two hands."
"I won't forgive that traitor who betrayed us, betrayed me and then left."
"Did Hadred have a reason for betraying me?"
"I have no idea, I don't understand! I wasn't there!"
"A betrayer is a betrayer! That's all I was informed of..."
"I didn't understand anything about him. That's what this boils down to!"
